-- Megatron / Switchblade --

Megatron gets out of his chair, then looks back at Flicker, "A 
shuttle isn't going to move, so we'll deal with it later. That or 
Switchblade could do something about it, right?" He glances at 
Switchblade, almost daring him to disagree, "Good, then bring the 
shuttle here, and then cover the defenses until we get back." Then 
notices that Perceptor wanted to say something.

"What is it Perceptor, we don't have all day." The Pred leader 
begins heading out of the control room, picking a path to the base 
exit.
